 new-found powers will you be able to deal with it.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2791440/extras/76d3108a7280a88c4623115763ba0018.avif?t=1752495018\" width=616 height=300 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2791440/extras/54d88a02b2831673c554d6c28a4989e7.webp?t=1752495018\" width=616 height=62 /></span><br>Learn a diverse range of professions, such as Fisher, Forager, Chef.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2791440/extras/9f213ae12f674c358d5b7edec77ecc97.avif?t=1752495018\" width=616 height=300 /></span><br><br>Woodcutter, Miner, Alchemist<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2791440/extras/84082ce1741ec4ee87300024438cbd6d.avif?t=1752495018\" width=616 height=300 /></span><br><br>Stonemason, Merchant, Blacksmith, and many more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2791440/extras/fae9c105f6648193c22233e0a9036efa.avif?t=1752495018\" width=616 height=300 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2791440/extras/b2a815d044925268ea8e2df5256164d1.webp?t=1752495018\" width=616 height=62 /></span><br>Encounter a huge variety of fantastical foes over the course of your adventures.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2791440/extras/98e24d652ad1f8578db107b54eb885f2.avif?t=1752495018\" width=616 height=300 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstati